# GestionSmataFC вЂ” Project Structure

A Next.js (App Router) + TypeScript application using Prisma with PostgreSQL for managing football team members, payments, expenses, and admin operations. Authentication uses JWT with refresh tokens; permissions are scoped per-team via `UserTeam`.

## Top-Level Layout

```
GestionSmataFC/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ .cursor/rules/         # Cursor AI rules (this folder)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ prisma/                # Database schema & migrations
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ public/                # Static assets (manifest.json)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ scripts/               # DB maintenance / ops scripts
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ src/                   # Application source code
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ .env                   # Local env vars (gitignored)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Dockerfile             # Production container build
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ next.config.js         # Next config; aliases `@` в†’ `src/`
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ next-env.d.ts          # Next type declarations
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ package.json           # Scripts & deps
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ tsconfig.json          # TS config; `@/*` в†’ `src/*`
в””в”Ђв”Ђ vitest.config.ts       # Vitest test runner config
```

