```

**Conventions:**
- All API endpoints live under `src/app/api/` as `route.ts` files (App Router).
- Dynamic params use the `[id]` folder convention.
- Admin-only endpoints are nested under `api/admin/` and should call permission helpers in [permissions.ts](mdc:src/lib/permissions.ts).

### `src/components/` вЂ” Presentational Components

Flat directory of `.tsx` UI components. Notable:
- [Dashboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/Dashboard.tsx), [Header.tsx](mdc:src/components/Header.tsx), [Nav.tsx](mdc:src/components/Nav.tsx), [Tabs.tsx](mdc:src/components/Tabs.tsx)
- Domain UI: [Payments.tsx](mdc:src/components/Payments.tsx), [Expenses.tsx](mdc:src/components/Expenses.tsx), [Participants.tsx](mdc:src/components/Participants.tsx), [Debtors.tsx](mdc:src/components/Debtors.tsx), [Comparison.tsx](mdc:src/components/Comparison.tsx)
- Admin UI: [AdminDashboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/AdminDashboard.tsx), [AdminUsers.tsx](mdc:src/components/AdminUsers.tsx), [AdminTeams.tsx](mdc:src/components/AdminTeams.tsx), [AdminUserTeams.tsx](mdc:src/components/AdminUserTeams.tsx), [AdminLogs.tsx](mdc:src/components/AdminLogs.tsx), [AdminStats.tsx](mdc:src/components/AdminStats.tsx)
- Utilities: [DarkModeToggle.tsx](mdc:src/components/DarkModeToggle.tsx), [Toast.tsx](mdc:src/components/Toast.tsx), [TeamSelector.tsx](mdc:src/components/TeamSelector.tsx), [MonthSelector.tsx](mdc:src/components/MonthSelector.tsx), [HistoryModal.tsx](mdc:src/components/HistoryModal.tsx)
- Barrel export: [index.tsx](mdc:src/components/index.tsx)

**Convention:** Components are pure/presentational where possible. Business logic and data fetching live in `containers/` or hooks.

### `src/containers/` вЂ” Stateful Wrappers

Smart components that orchestrate hooks + services and render the matching `components/` UI.

- [DashboardContainer.tsx](mdc:src/containers/DashboardContainer.tsx)
- [PaymentsContainer.tsx](mdc:src/containers/PaymentsContainer.tsx), [ExpensesContainer.tsx](mdc:src/containers/ExpensesContainer.tsx), [ParticipantsContainer.tsx](mdc:src/containers/ParticipantsContainer.tsx)
- [DebtorsContainer.tsx](mdc:src/containers/DebtorsContainer.tsx), [ComparisonContainer.tsx](mdc:src/containers/ComparisonContainer.tsx)
- [SettingsContainer.tsx](mdc:src/containers/SettingsContainer.tsx), [HistoryModalContainer.tsx](mdc:src/containers/HistoryModalContainer.tsx), [MonthlyProgressBarContainer.tsx](mdc:src/containers/MonthlyProgressBarContainer.tsx)
- Barrel: [index.ts](mdc:src/containers/index.ts)

**Convention:** Pages/routes import containers (not raw components) for any stateful section.

### `src/context/` вЂ” React Contexts

- [UserContext.tsx](mdc:src/context/UserContext.tsx) вЂ” current authenticated user
- [TeamDataContext.tsx](mdc:src/context/TeamDataContext.tsx) вЂ” active team + cached data

### `src/hooks/` вЂ” Reusable React Hooks

- Data hooks: [useExpenses.ts](mdc:src/hooks/useExpenses.ts), [usePayments.ts](mdc:src/hooks/usePayments.ts), [useParticipants.ts](mdc:src/hooks/useParticipants.ts), [useTeamData.ts](mdc:src/hooks/useTeamData.ts), [useConfig.ts](mdc:src/hooks/useConfig.ts)
