### `src/lib/` вЂ” Server & Shared Utilities

Cross-cutting modules used by API routes and (sometimes) the client.

- [db.ts](mdc:src/lib/db.ts) вЂ” Prisma client singleton
- [auth.ts](mdc:src/lib/auth.ts), [jwt.ts](mdc:src/lib/jwt.ts) вЂ” Auth + token helpers
- [permissions.ts](mdc:src/lib/permissions.ts) вЂ” Role / team access checks
- [api-response.ts](mdc:src/lib/api-response.ts) вЂ” Standardized API JSON responses
- [httpClient.ts](mdc:src/lib/httpClient.ts) вЂ” Fetch wrapper for client calls
- [schemas.ts](mdc:src/lib/schemas.ts) вЂ” Zod validation schemas
- [audit.ts](mdc:src/lib/audit.ts), [logger.ts](mdc:src/lib/logger.ts) вЂ” Audit log + structured logging
- [rateLimit.ts](mdc:src/lib/rateLimit.ts) вЂ” Rate-limit middleware
- [env.ts](mdc:src/lib/env.ts) вЂ” Validated env vars
- [utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts) вЂ” Generic helpers
- `domain/` вЂ” Pure business logic (with co-located `*.test.ts` Vitest files)
  - [debt.ts](mdc:src/lib/domain/debt.ts), [expenses.ts](mdc:src/lib/domain/expenses.ts), [history.ts](mdc:src/lib/domain/history.ts), [participantStats.ts](mdc:src/lib/domain/participantStats.ts), [summary.ts](mdc:src/lib/domain/summary.ts)
- `utils/` вЂ” Domain-adjacent helpers, e.g. [whatsapp.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils/whatsapp.ts)

**Convention:** Pure, framework-free business logic belongs in `lib/domain/` and is the only place tests are co-located.

### `src/services/` вЂ” Client-side API Layer

Thin wrappers over `httpClient` that expose typed CRUD operations to containers/hooks.

- [payments.ts](mdc:src/services/payments.ts), [expenses.ts](mdc:src/services/expenses.ts), [participants.ts](mdc:src/services/participants.ts), [config.ts](mdc:src/services/config.ts)
- [types.ts](mdc:src/services/types.ts), barrel [index.ts](mdc:src/services/index.ts)

### `src/types/` вЂ” Shared Types

- [index.ts](mdc:src/types/index.ts) вЂ” exported app-wide TS types/interfaces

## `prisma/` вЂ” Database

- [schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) вЂ” single source of truth for the data model. Key models: `Team`, `User`, `UserTeam`, `Participant`, `Payment`, `Expense`, `Config`, `MonthlyConfig`, `ParticipantMonthlyStatus`, `AuditLog`.
- `migrations/` вЂ” generated migrations (gitignored except `migration_lock.toml`)

## `scripts/` вЂ” Ops Scripts

Standalone Node/PowerShell scripts run outside Next.js:
- [backup-db.ps1](mdc:scripts/backup-db.ps1) / [backup-db.sh](mdc:scripts/backup-db.sh) вЂ” DB dumps
- [createUser.js](mdc:scripts/createUser.js), [listUsers.js](mdc:scripts/listUsers.js), [clearLoginAttempts.js](mdc:scripts/clearLoginAttempts.js), [dbCounts.js](mdc:scripts/dbCounts.js)

## Key Configuration Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) вЂ” scripts: `dev`, `build` (runs `prisma generate` first), `start`, `test` (Vitest), `lint`, `db:migrate`, `db:push`, `db:seed`
- [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js) вЂ” Webpack alias `@` в†’ `src/`; Turbopack root pinned
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) вЂ” `baseUrl: "src"`, path alias `@/*` в†’ `*`
- [vitest.config.ts](mdc:vitest.config.ts) вЂ” Vitest configuration
- [Dockerfile](mdc:Dockerfile) вЂ” production image build

## Import Conventions

Always use the `@/` alias (mapped to `src/`) instead of relative paths that traverse upward:

```typescript
// Good
import { prisma } from '@/lib/db';
import { Dashboard } from '@/components/Dashboard';
import { useTeamData } from '@/hooks/useTeamData';

// Bad
import { prisma } from '../../../lib/db';
import { Dashboard } from '../../components/Dashboard';
```

## Where to Put New Code

| New code type                        | Location                              |
| ------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------- |
| New page/route                       | `src/app/<segment>/page.tsx`          |
| New API endpoint                     | `src/app/api/<segment>/route.ts`      |
| Admin-only API endpoint              | `src/app/api/admin/<segment>/route.ts`|
| Pure UI component                    | `src/components/<Name>.tsx`           |
| Stateful wrapper for a section       | `src/containers/<Name>Container.tsx`  |
| Reusable hook                        | `src/hooks/use<Name>.ts`              |
| Client-side API caller               | `src/services/<resource>.ts`          |
| Pure business logic + unit tests     | `src/lib/domain/<name>.ts` (+ `.test.ts`) |
| Server util (auth, db, validationвЂ¦)  | `src/lib/<name>.ts`                   |
| Shared TS types                      | `src/types/index.ts`                  |
| Prisma model change                  | `prisma/schema.prisma` (+ migration)  |
| One-off DB / ops script              | `scripts/<name>.{js,ps1,sh}`          |

## Forbidden / Avoid

- Do not place tests outside `src/lib/domain/` unless extending the test setup.
- Do not import from `.next/`, `node_modules/`, or generated files directly.
- Do not bypass [permissions.ts](mdc:src/lib/permissions.ts) in `api/admin/*` or team-scoped routes.
- Do not create new top-level folders under `src/`; reuse the existing 8 directories.
